This paper is likely to belong to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category as it deals with evolutionary algorithms and fitness optimization. It could also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category as it proposes a new selection scheme for optimization. Additionally, it could be classified under Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) as it deals with optimization techniques. The paper also involves data structures (cs.DS) as it discusses the genetic diversity of populations. Finally, it could be classified under Systems and Control (cs.SY) as it deals with optimization in a system.
